BuildRequires:    R-devel
Requires:         R-core
BuildArch:        noarch
BuildRequires:    R-CRAN-fftw 
Requires:         R-CRAN-fftw 

%description
Implements multinomial CDF (P(N1<=n1, ..., Nk<=nk)) and tail probabilities
(P(N1>n1, ..., Nk>nk)), as well as probabilities with both constraints
(P(l1<N1<=u1, ..., lk<Nk<=uk)). Uses a method suggested by Bruce Levin
(1981) <doi:10.1214/aos/1176345593>.

